    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The plant has large, toothed, motile leaves that it usually keeps hidden until something disturbs them. Once triggered, the leaves slash viciously at anything thrust among them. A branch or vine fitted with these leaves usually carries 6-8 of them, and each such branch inflicts 1d4 damage per melee turn. They cut only cloth, flesh, and other soft materials.</p>"
